Author: Frederic Bertrand [cre, aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0837-8281>), Fatima Fahs [aut], Myriam Maumy-Bertrand [aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4615-1512>)
Maintainer: Frederic Bertrand <frederic.bertrand@lecnam.net>
Description: Implements Kernel Wavelet Functional (KWF),
    Generalized Additive Models (GAM), Multivariate Adaptive
    Regression Splines (MARS) and RNN LSTM models to forecast
    individual electricity load curves, following the methodology
    described in Fahs (2023) and related articles and posters.
    Includes small demo datasets and helper functions to download
    large public datasets such as ELMAS, StoreNet Ireland and IDEAL.
